title: TypeError: __init__() got an unexpected keyword argument 'target_tensor'
body_html:
here is my code:
import torch import torch.utils.data as Data x = torch.linspace(1,10,10) y = torch.linspae(10,1,10) dataset = Data.TensorDataset(data_tensor=x,target_tensor=y)
and it give my a TypeError: init() got an unexpected keyword argument 'target_tensor'
my python version is 2.7.15 and torch version is 0.4.0
